description: Gua Pass is a Membership card issued by Gua DAO, the first investment-focused DAO for Bitcoin Ordinals. 'Gua' is a Web3 culture that has spontaneously formed within the Pixel Pepes community. Holders of Gua Pass can participate in the development and operation of Gua DAO, share investment returns, and continuously receive surprise airdrops.
name: Gua PASS
